        <description>Supers with this power are able to summon a ball of ice explodes to rapidly freeze opponents.\n\nThis doesn't render you immune to ice, so remember to get protection.</description>
        <iconPath>Powers/Gene_IceBall</iconPath>
        <displayOrderInCategory>31</displayOrderInCategory>
        <abilities>
            <li>SHG_IceBlast</li>
